$$\exists P. (P a) \supset (p b)$$

```elixir
a = mk_const_term("a", type_i)
p = mk_free_var("P", type_io)
p_term = mk_term(p)

p2 = mk_const_term("p", type_io)
b = mk_const_term("b", type_i)

p_b = mk_appl_term(p2, b)

p_a = mk_appl_term(p_term, a)
implication = mk_appl_term(mk_appl_term(implies_term, p_a), p_b)
lambda_p = mk_abstr_term(implication, p)
