unify({line_19, neg_line_18}) |> PrettyPrint.pp_res()
```

## Appendix C: Functional Extensionality by Hand

0\. $\Pi_{oo(\iota\iota)}(\lambda F_{\iota\iota}. \Pi_{oo(\iota\iota)}(\lambda G_{\iota\iota}. \supset (\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (F_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (G_{\iota\iota} X_\iota))) (=_{o(\iota\iota)(\iota\iota)} F_{\iota\iota} G_{\iota\iota})))$

1\. $\neg\Pi_{oo(\iota\iota)}(\lambda F_{\iota\iota}. \Pi_{oo(\iota\iota)}(\lambda G_{\iota\iota}. \supset (\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (F_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (G_{\iota\iota} X_\iota))) (=_{o(\iota\iota)(\iota\iota)} F_{\iota\iota} G_{\iota\iota})))$ $\quad$ Tableaux initialization

2\. $\Pi_{oo(\iota\iota)}(\lambda G_{\iota\iota}. \supset (\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (G_{\iota\iota} X_\iota))) (=_{o(\iota\iota)(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} G_{\iota\iota}))$ $\quad$ $\neg\Pi (1)$

3\. $\supset (\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota))) (=_{o(\iota\iota)(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota})$ $\quad$ $\Pi (2)$

_Branch A:_

4\. $\neg(\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota)))$ $\quad$ $\supset (3)$

5\. $\neg(=_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota})) (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota})))$ $\quad$ $\neg\Pi (4)$

6\. $\neg(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)}(\lambda P_{o\iota}. \equiv (P_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}))) (P_{o\iota} (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota})))))$ $\quad$ $\neg= (5)$

7\. $\neg(\equiv ((\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}))) ((\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}))))$ $\quad$ $\neg \Pi (6)$

_Branch AA:_

8\. $\neg ((\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota})))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (7)$

9\. $(\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota}))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (7)$

$\star (8, 9)$ with $\sigma_{AA} = \{\mathbf{X}^1_{\iota\iota} \gets \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota}\}$

_Branch AB: (including $\sigma_{AA}$)_

10\. $(\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota}))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (7)$

11\. $\neg((\mathbf{sk}^3_{o\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota}) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^2_{\iota(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota})))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (7)$

$\star (10, 11)$ with $\sigma_{AB} = \sigma_{AA} \cup \varnothing$

_Branch B: (including $\sigma_{AB}$)_

12\. $=_{o(\iota\iota)(\iota\iota)} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota}$ $\quad$ $\supset (3)$

13\. $\Pi_{oo\iota}(\lambda X_\iota. =_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} X_\iota))$ $\quad$ $= (12)$

14\. $=_{o\iota\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\Pi (13)$

15\. $\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \equiv (P_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)) (P_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)))$ $\quad$ $= (14)$

16\. $\equiv (\mathbf{X}^3_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)) (\mathbf{X}^3_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota))$ $\quad$ $\Pi (15)$

_Branch BA:_

17\. $\mathbf{X}^3_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\equiv (16)$

18\. $\mathbf{X}^3_{o\iota} (\mathbf{sk}^1_{\iota\iota} \mathbf{X}^2_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\equiv (16)$

cannot close branch without reinstantiating

```elixir
# unification for branch AA
sk1 = mk_const_term("sk1", type_ii)
sk2 = mk_const_term("sk2", mk_type(type_i, [type_ii]))
sk3 = mk_const_term("sk3", mk_type(type_io, [type_ii]))
x1 = mk_free_var_term("X1", type_ii)

sk3_x1 = mk_appl_term(sk3, x1)
sk2_x1 = mk_appl_term(sk2, x1)
sk1_sk2_x1 = mk_appl_term(sk1, sk2_x1)
x1_sk2_x1 = mk_appl_term(x1, sk2_x1)

neg_line_8 = mk_appl_term(sk3_x1, sk1_sk2_x1)
line_9 = mk_appl_term(sk3_x1, x1_sk2_x1)

PrettyPrint.pp_term(neg_line_8) |> IO.puts()
PrettyPrint.pp_term(line_9) |> IO.puts()

res = unify({neg_line_8, line_9})
PrettyPrint.pp_res(res)
```

```elixir
# attempted unification for branch BA
x3 = mk_free_var_term("X3", type_io)
x2 = mk_free_var_term("X2", type_i)

sk1_x2 = mk_appl_term(sk1, x2)
x3_sk1_x2 = mk_appl_term(x3, sk1_x2)

neg_line_17 = mk_appl_term(neg_term, x3_sk1_x2)
line_18 = x3_sk1_x2

PrettyPrint.pp_term(neg_line_17) |> IO.puts()
PrettyPrint.pp_term(line_18) |> IO.puts()

res = unify({neg_line_17, line_18})
PrettyPrint.pp_res(res)
```

## Appendix D: Leibnitz Equality by Hand

0\. $\equiv (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))~(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a)))$

1\. $\neg(\equiv (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))~(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a))))$ $\quad$ Tableaux initialization

_Branch A:_

2\. $\neg (\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota)))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

3\. $\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b_\iota) (P_{o\iota} a_\iota))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

4\. $\supset (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota) (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\neg\Pi (2)$

_Branch AA:_

5\. $\neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (4)$

6\. $\supset (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota) (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} a)$ $\quad$ $\Pi (3)$

_Branch AAA:_

7\. $\neg (\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (6)$

$\star$ with $\sigma^1 = \{\mathbf{X}^1_{o\iota} \gets (\lambda X_\iota. \neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota))\}$

_Branch AAB (including $\sigma^1$):_

8\. $\neg (\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} a_\iota)$ $\quad$ $\supset (6)$

Reinstantiation necessary

_Branch AB:_

?\. $\mathbf{sk}^1_{o\iota} b_\iota$ $\quad$ $\supset (4)$

_Branch B:_

?\. $\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} a_\iota) (P_{o\iota} b_\iota))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

??\. $\neg(\Pi_{oo(o\iota)} (\lambda P_{o\iota}. \supset (P_{o\iota} b) (P_{o\iota} a)))$ $\quad$ $\neg\equiv (1)$

```elixir
# unification to close branch AAA:
a = mk_const_term("a", type_i)
b = mk_const_term("b", type_i)
sk1 = mk_const_term("sk1", type_io)
x1 = mk_free_var_term("X1", type_io)

neg_line_5 = mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(sk1, a)))
line_7 = mk_appl_term(neg_term, mk_appl_term(x1, b))

PrettyPrint.pp_term(neg_line_5) |> IO.puts()
PrettyPrint.pp_term(line_7) |> IO.puts()

unify({line_7, neg_line_5}) |> PrettyPrint.pp_res()
```

